description: This file defines a Java interface for accessing 'FinetuneJob' entities from a database, extending JpaRepository for CRUD operations and including a custom method to find jobs by their status.

classes.name: FinetuneJobRepository
classes.description: A Spring Data JPA repository interface for managing FinetuneJob entities with an additional method to find jobs by status.

methods.name: findByStatus
methods.description: Retrieves a list of FinetuneJob entities filtered by a specific status.
